data.description: Discover affordability and charm in this 3-bed, 1-bath gem, featuring a detached garage and parking slab. With a smart layout and finished basement boasting a stylish bar, this home offers both comfort and entertainment space. The well-appointed bedrooms and fully-equipped kitchen cater to modern living. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this property is your ticket to a comfortable lifestyle without breaking the bank.
